### 5. LINX Memory Sync to ROSA - 🟥
**Description:** LINX memory syncs to ROSA for meta-analysis
**Expected Behavior:**
- Memory sent to ROSA via remember_with_rosa()
- ROSA receives full memory dict (content, emotion, importance, context)
- ROSA processes memory successfully
- Returns analysis dict to LINX
